<span class="name"><a name="459234"></a></span><span class="postdetails">#43:&nbsp;<font color=black><b></b> Автор:&nbsp;<b>mdfv</b>,&nbsp;</font></span><span class="postdetails"><font color=black></font></span>
<a href="post_459234.html#459234"><img src="templates/fisubgreen/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" class="imgspace" width="12" height="9" alt="Сообщение" title="Сообщение" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails"><font color=black>Добавлено: Вт 13 Мар 2007, 21:38</font><span class="gen"><br>
